  "keyFeatures": [
    "FOC (Field Oriented Control) motor control with sensorless, Hall sensor, and encoder modes",
    "BLDC (Brushless DC) trapezoidal commutation support",
    "LispBM scripting environment for custom applications running on the VESC",
    "CAN-bus multi-device communication and control",
    "Wide hardware support: Trampa, FlipSky, MakerX, Ubox, and many more",
    "Multiple encoder support: ABI, AS504x, SinCos, BiSSC, PWM, and more",
    "IMU integration: BMI160, ICM20948, LSM6DS3, MPU9150",
    "USB, UART, and CAN communication interfaces",
    "Configurable input applications: PPM, ADC, UART, Nunchuk, PAS",
    "Over-the-air (OTA) firmware updates via VESC Tool"
  ],
